  <compounddef id="UDPLASTIP" kind="page">
    <compoundname>UDPLASTIP</compoundname>
    <title>UDPLASTIP$ Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">UDPLASTIP$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Returns the <bold>source IP address</bold> (as a dotted-quad string) of the <bold>most recent packet</bold> returned by <ref refid="UDPREAD" kindref="compound">UDPREAD$</ref>.</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>If no packet has been read yet, returns <computeroutput>&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect3 id="UDPLASTIP_1autotoc_md676">
<title>How to read it</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Call <bold>after</bold> <computeroutput>UDPREAD$</computeroutput> to determine the sender of the payload you just received.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="UDPLASTIP_1autotoc_md678">
<title>Examples</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">UDPBIND<sp/>&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;,<sp/>8080</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">S$<sp/>=<sp/>UDPREAD$(8080)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">IF<sp/>LEN(S$)<sp/>&gt;<sp/>0<sp/>THEN</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>PRINT<sp/>&quot;Packet<sp/>received<sp/>from<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>UDPLASTIP$</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ENDIF</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="UDPLASTIP_1autotoc_md680">
<title>Notes</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The value updates only when <ref refid="UDPREAD" kindref="compound">UDPREAD$</ref> dequeues a packet.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Always returns the sender’s IPv4 address in dotted decimal form (<computeroutput>a.b.c.d</computeroutput>).</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="UDPREAD" kindref="compound">UDPREAD$</ref> · <ref refid="UDPLASTSOURCEPORT" kindref="compound">UDPLASTSOURCEPORT</ref> </para>
</sect3>
